Exciting news! ✨ Our partnership with @truemedpayments allows you to usie your Health Savings Account (HSA) or Flexible Savings Acount (FSA) to purchase Juna, even your MicrobiomelQ gut health test! That means shopping with pre-tax dollars, resulting in a net savings of 30% on average for you.
